                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If a redcap sees a creature brandish a religious symbol of a deity (which requires an Interact action by that creature) or cast a divine spell while wearing a religious symbol, the redcap must attempt a @Check[will|dc:24] save. The DC is @Check[will|dc:26] against a symbol of Shelyn and @Check[will|dc:34] against his lucky dawnsilver corkscrew.</p>\n<p>They then become temporarily immune to all brandished religious symbols for 10 minutes.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The redcap is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The redcap is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The redcap gains the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Fleeing] condition for 1 round and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 4}.</p>"
                },
