                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature Brensen can see within 30 feet spends an action retching in an attempt to recover from the sickened condition and fails</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Brensen points and laughs at the triggering creature, causing their sickened condition value to increase by 1, or to fall @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone] if their sickened condition value is already @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 3}.</p>"
