                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Brensen takes a deep gulp of alcohol, then winks at a creature he can see within 30 feet. The alcohol he imbibed suddenly infuses the belly of the target, causing them to attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:25] save with the following effects.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} and falls @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone].</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} as long as it's remain sickened.</p>"
                },
